Package com.ulflander.mining.processors.extract

Processors that extract and format document into an analyzable model.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
DocumentCleaner Processor that clean a document, intended to run as first processor.
DocumentSplitter Processor that split a document into chapters, and paragraphs.
LanguageDetector Detects language of a document on the global document, then on each sentences.
OpenNLPTokenizer Processor that tokenize a sentence (Using Apache OpenNLP).
POSTagger Processor that detects part of speech in text (Using Stanford POSTagger).
RawArticleCleaner Processor that cleanup article contents fromInternet slang such as "Read comments".
TokenCleaner Processor that clean a token.
TokenGuessConsolidation Processor that consolidates token type.
TokenListGuesser Compare each token to a list of names and add score for token that looks like a name part.
TokenRegExpGuesser Processor that attempt to give a type to tokens.
